    "feat": {
        "name": "Eagle Eyes",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You and your spotter are adept at watching out for one another. As long as you can see or hear each other, neither of you is flat-footed to hidden, undetected, or flanking creatures of your level or lower, or to creatures of your level or lower using a surprise attack. However, they can still help their allies flank.",
